The 20 May 2011 edition of Noticias 123 (in Spanish
http://noticias.123.cl/noticias/20110520_bf107340efb6320df6b2d2f3ae9faf9a.htm)
reported that the man collected wood [presumably in the forest], an
important piece of his history. To date, there have been 6 cases of
[a] hantavirus infection, all male, 4 of whom died].

