[3] Argentina (Entre Rios)
Date: Sun 22 May 2011
Source: El Argentino [in Spanish, trans. Mod.TY, edited]
http://www.diarioelargentino.com.ar/noticias/91683/son-cuatro-los-casos-confirmados-por-hanta-virus


The provincial Director of Epidemiology, Silvina Saavedra, stated
that to date, 4 positive cases of hantavirus [infections] have been
confirmed in Victoria [Entre Rios province], of whom 2 died and the
other 2 recovered and were released [from the hospital].

Saavedra commented that the laboratory results were awaited for other
cases. "These are samples that were sent some time ago," she explained
in dialog with this news agency, adding that "the results come in
continuously, and are updated."

